 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Configuration-file for the Password Plugin for Roundcube
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------

 This configuration file is for the password plugin for Roundcube and
 allows Froxlor users to change their e-mail password within Roundcube.

 -----------------------------------------------------------------------

 You only have to edit one thing:

 Look for:

 $config['password_db_dsn'] = 'mysql://froxlor:MYSQL_PASSWORD@localhost/froxlor';

 and replace MYSQL_PASSWORD with the password for the froxlor-database-user.

 
 If you do not want plaintext-passwords to be stored in the database,
 edit $rcmail_config['password_query'] and remove "`password` = %p,"

